PCNSA 10

updated: 7th of February 2021

published: 1st of January 2021

Intro

My number one certification goal for 2021 is the PCNSA 10 certification. I require it for my new role so I am getting stuck right in.

In this post I will document the resources and links to my personal notes for the PCNSA 10 certification.

I will update this document as I go up until I have passed the certification.
